---
description: Keep documentation, READMEs, and rules accurate and updated
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

- When you make changes to a package/directory, make sure its docs stay up to date.
- Do not reference transient project tasks, milestone names, or ticket IDs in code comments or long-term design documents. Enforce stable names.
- If you introduce a new design pattern, document it under `docs/architecture/patterns/`.
- Ensure all rules index tables reflect added rulecards.